  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study shall evaluate in daily medical practice the clinical results of the AV delay
      hysteresis search algorithm in patients with a INSIGNIA ULTRA or AVT pacemaker implanted for
      one of the three following indications: sinus node dysfunction, atrial disease (or
      bradycardia/tachycardia) and atrio-ventricular paroxysmal block. In addition use and outcome
      of automatic functions will be evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
